<div id="complexheadercontent">
<h1><a href="/node/25">Introducing Scala</a></h1>
<p>Scala is a general purpose programming language designed to express common programming patterns in a concise, elegant, and type-safe way. It smoothly integrates features of object-oriented and functional languages, enabling Java and other programmers to be more productive. Code sizes are typically reduced by a factor of two to three when compared to an equivalent Java application.&nbsp;&nbsp; <a href="/node/25"><strong>Read&nbsp;more</strong></a></p>
</div>
</div></div></div>
</div>
                            <h1 class="title"></h1>
              <div class="tabs"></div>
                                          <div class="view view-frontpagescala view-id-frontpagescala view-display-id-page view-dom-id-1">
        <div class="view-header">
